titleNullable: Recalls Data from US Department of Transportation
subtitleNullable: Recall information related to specific NHTSA campaigns
descriptionNullable:
The dataset includes recall information related to specific NHTSA campaigns. Users can filter based on characteristics like manufacturer and component. The dataset can also be filtered by recall type: tires, vehicles, car seats, and equipment. The earliest campaign data is from 1966.

Source: https://datahub.transportation.gov/Automobiles/Recalls-Data/6axg-epim
